          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Case%20Studies/6.png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Case Study" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Case%20Studies/1.png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Case Study" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Case%20Studies/2.png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Case Study" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Case%20Studies/3.png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Case Study" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Testimonials/Testo.png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Testimonial" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Testimonials/Testo%20(1).png?tr=w-1400,q-100,f-webp" alt="Testimonial" loading="lazy" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="tp-container">
 
      <p class="about-subhead">Here's how it works:</p>
      <ol class="about-steps">
        <li>
          <div class="about-step-content">
            <span>Droparabia finds you winning products that have demand in the Lebanese market</span>
            <img src="/1.png" alt="" class="about-step-img" />
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="about-step-content">
            <span>You add the product you want to sell to your own website with a click</span>
            <img src="/2.png" alt="" class="about-step-img" />
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><span>Droparabia handles packaging and order delivery when a customer orders from you</span></li>
        
        <li><span>You only pay per product sold and collect the profit through Whish account</span></li>
      </ol>
      <p class="about-closing">While you focus only on marketing and advertising</p>

      <div class="cta-block">
        <a href="/survey" class="cta-btn" id="cta2">
          <span class="cta-btn-main">Start selling with Droparabia!</span>
