        <li><span>+20 Hours of FREE Courses &amp; Recorded Tutorials inside our community</span></li>
        <li><span>Support from our Team of Experts + Our own AI assistant built in Droparabia</span></li>
        <li><span>2 Weekly Coaching Calls to provide you feedback and track your progress</span></li>
        <li class="bonuses-list-plus"><span><span class="bonuses-plus-label">PLUS:</span> If a product you want to sell is not available on Droparabia, we will <span class="bonuses-highlight">find &amp; source it for you</span> without extra fees!</span></li>
